      <p>A <a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">wight's</a> appearance is a weird and twisted reflection of the form it had in life. A <a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">wight</a> is about the height and weight of a human.<a href="img/MonstersT-Z.Wight.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersT-Z.Wight.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p><a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">Wights</a> speak Common.</p>
