        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z109"/>
        <p><a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">Wights</a> attack by hammering with their fists.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2235927"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z110"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Create Spawn (Su):</strong></span> Any humanoid slain by a <a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">wight</a> becomes a <a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">wight</a> in 1d4 rounds. Spawn are under the command of the <a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">wight</a> that created them and remain enslaved until its death. They do not possess any of the abilities they had in life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2236055"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z111"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Energy Drain (Su):</strong></span> Living creatures hit by a <a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">wight's</a> slam attack gain one negative level. The DC is 14 for the Fortitude save to remove a negative level. The save DC is Charisma-based. For each such negative level bestowed, the <a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">wight</a> gains 5 temporary hit points.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2236106"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z112"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> <a href="ch72s13.html#MonstersT-Z108">Wights</a> have a +8 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills211">Move Silently</a> checks.</p>
